# endProgress

**Instance Property**

Indicates the end point of the receiver as a fraction of the entire transition.

## Declaration

```swift
var endProgress: Float { get set }
```

## Discussion

The value must be greater than or equal to [doc://com.apple.quartzcore/documentation/QuartzCore/CATransition/startProgress], and not greater than 1.0.  If `endProgress` is less than [doc://com.apple.quartzcore/documentation/QuartzCore/CATransition/startProgress] the behavior is undefined. The default value is 1.0.

## Transition start and end point

- **startProgress**: Indicates the start point of the receiver as a fraction of the entire transition.
